---
title: Red Pepper Glazed Chermoula Chicken with Courgette, Couscous and Dill Yoghurt Drizzle
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Red Pepper Glazed Chermoula Chicken in just 20 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R12_W18_UK_QR13724-5_Main_low-21ef79f6.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/red-pepper-glazed-chermoula-chicken-63fe37a262bd092a2131203f-e4d3499c.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/red-pepper-glazed-chermoula-chicken-63fe37a262bd092a2131203f
time required: 20 minutes
author: Anushka Magan
servings: 2
course: main course
